##CPGE_SCRIPT
##ScriptVersion: 1.0
##Written: 2026-05-10
##Scene: SCENE_INITIALISE
##Author: LordAries1972
##Description: Engine cold-start sequence — precache load, default camera, audio init.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Load precached scene data if available
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
LOAD

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Default camera
# POSITION x y z yaw pitch
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
POSITION 0.0 0.0 -10.0 0.0 0.0

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Start audio subsystem immediately
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute StartPlaybackThread()
Execute SetGlobalVolume(1.0)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Fade from black (engine is coming up)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute FadeToBlack(0.0, 0.0)
Execute FadeToImage(1.0, 0.5)

ALERT General "Engine initialised successfully."
